.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking water##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | water  | hot-chocolate    | lemonade | iced-tea    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse    | dog        | horse   |

