.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, september, march
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is between the person who's birthday is in september and the argentine##2
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the australian##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person who's birthday is in april##1
9. the turkish is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday      | april | september      | january  | march    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Pet           | turtle      | pony       | horse   | goat      |

