.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, train, boat
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person driving the quad-bike##2
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
6. the japanese is between the person driving the quad-bike and the australian##2
7. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Transport         | train   | quad-bike      | boat | scooter       |

