.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, ivory, fuchsia, purple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, swimming, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
5. the person who likes ivory is between the person driving the bike and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes white##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color    | fuchsia    | ivory     | white    | purple        |
| Sport       | swimming   | baseball | surfing | water-polo |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

